The paper discusses a new language and compiler for Fully-Homomorphic Encryption (FHE), which is a topic in cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the constrained programming model and unusual performance profile of FHE, indicating a focus on programming languages (cs.PL). The development of image processing applications using EVA suggests a focus on machine learning and computer vision (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the potential for EVA to be used as an intermediate representation for domain-specific languages, indicating a focus on software engineering (cs.SE) and systems (cs.SY).
